These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, traveling
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, july
2 different games are played: snooker, monopoly
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Hobby           | traveling | writing |
| Birthday   | july     | may   |
| Game   | monopoly  | snooker     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Transport     | roller     | van        |

