.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower
House: modern, futuristic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, handball
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person drinking water is the futuristic house##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping |
| Flower   | bellflower     | sunflower   |
| House   | modern       | futuristic     |
| Sport           | handball        | skateboarding    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

